H\degree_f(CH3OH)=\qty{716}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}+\qty{872}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}+\qty{248}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}-\qty{1236}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}-\qty{360}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}-\qty{463}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}\]}
{\[\Delta H\degree_f(CH3OH)=\qty{-223}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}\]}

{\[\Delta
H\degree_f(\ce{K2S_{(s)}})=2\Delta H\degree_{sub}(\ce{K})+2\Delta
H\degree_{ion}(\ce{K})+\Delta H\degree_{sub}(\ce{S})+\Delta
H\degree_{ge}(\ce{S})+\Delta H\degree_{ge}(\ce{S^-})+\Delta
H\degree_{rede}(\ce{K2S})\]}
{\[\qty{-381}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}=\qty{180}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}+\pu{8 eV 6,02\cdot 10^{23} mol^{-1} 1,6\cdot
10^{-22}\frac{kJ}{eV}}+\qty{277}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}+(\pu{-2 eV 6,02\cdot 10^{23}
mol^{-1} 1,6\cdot 10^{-22}\frac{kJ}{eV}})+\Delta
H\degree_{ge}(\ce{S^-})+(\qty{-2050}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}})\]} {\[\pu{E_{ae2}(\ce{S}) 6,02\cdot 10^{23} mol^{-1}
1,6\cdot 10^{-22}\frac{kJ}{eV}}=\qty{634,08}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}\implies
E_{ae2}(\ce{S})\approx\qty{6,583}{\unit{eV}}\]}

Combustão completa do octano gasoso: {\[\ce{C8H18 + \frac{25}{2}O2 -> 8CO2 +
9H2O}\]} {\[\Delta H_C=7\Delta
H_L(\ce{C-C})+18\Delta H_L(\ce{C-H})+\frac{25}{2}\Delta
H_L(\ce{O2})-(16\Delta H_L(\ce{C=O})+18\Delta H_L(\ce{O-H}))\]}
{\[\Delta H_C=7\cdot\qty{348}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}+18\cdot\qty{412}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}+\frac{25}{2}\cdot\qty{496}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}-16\cdot\qty{803}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}-18\cdot\qty{463}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}\]}
{\[\Delta H_C=\qty{-5130}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}\implies\frac{\Delta
H_C}{N(H)}=\qty{-285}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}\]} Célula de combustível de hidrogênio e oxigênio: {\[\ce{H2 +
\frac{1}{2}O2 -> H2O}\]} {\[\Delta
H=\Delta H_L(\ce{H2})+\frac{1}{2}\Delta H_L(\ce{O2})-2\Delta
H_L(\unit{O-H})\]}
{\[\Delta H=\qty{463}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}+\qty{248}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}-\qty{926}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}\]}
{\[\Delta H=\qty{-215}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}\implies\frac{\Delta
H}{N(H)}=\qty{-107,5}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}\]} Logo, a razão pedida é dada por:
{\[r=\frac{\qty{-285}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}}{\qty{-107,5}{\tfrac{\unit{kJ}}{\unit{mol}}}}\approx 2,65\]}

