  {\(\ce{HCl}\)} : Dipolo-dipolo. {\(\ce{NaCl}\)} : Ligação iônica. {\(T_{eb}\)} ({\(\ce{HCl}\)}) \textless{} {\(T_{eb}\)} ({\(\ce{NaCl}\)})
