  \ce{(NH4)2SO4}}=\frac{m_{\ce{(NH4)2SO4}}}{m _\text{total}}\]}
  {\[\%_{m, \ce{(NH4)2SO4}}=\frac{\qty{264}{\unit{mg}}}{\qty{1200}{\unit{mg}}}=\boxed{22\%}\]}
\item
  Cálculo da fração mássica de {\(\ce{NH4NO3}\)} : {\[\%_{m, \ce{NH4NO3}}=\frac{m_{\ce{NH4NO3}}}{m
  _\text{total}}\]} {\[\%_{m,
  \ce{NH4NO3}}=\frac{\qty{320}{\unit{mg}}}{\qty{1200}{\unit{mg}}}=\boxed{26,7\%}\]}
\end{itemize}

