solution.tex:
Cálculo das concentrações de cada íon com base na estequiometria do composto{\((\ce{Na2SO4})\)}
{\[\frac{\ce{c_{\ce{Na^{+}}}}}{2}=\frac{c_{\ce{SO4^{2-}}}}{1}=\frac{c_{\ce{Na2SO4}}}{1}\]} Portanto: {\[c_{\ce{Na^{+}}}=\qty{0,02}{\unit{mol
L^{-1}}}=\qty{0,02}{\unit{M}}\]} {\[c_{\ce{SO4^{2-}}}=\qty{0,01}{\unit{mol L^{-1}}}=\qty{0,01}{\unit{M}}\]} Cálculo da condutividade a partir das
condutividades dos íons: {\[\kappa=\sum\limits \lambda c\]} {\[\kappa=\lambda(\ce{Na+})(c_{\ce{Na^{+}}})+\lambda(\ce{SO4^{2-}})(c_{\ce{SO4^{2-}}})\]}
{\[\kappa=(\qty{5}{\unit{S m^{-1} M^{-1}}})(\qty{0,02}{\unit{M}})+(\qty{16}{\unit{S m^{-1} M^{-1}}})(\qty{0,01}{\unit{M}})\]}
{\[\kappa=\qty{0,26}{\unit{S m^{-1}}}\]}

